INSERT INTO `#__content`  VALUES ('1', '61', 'Home', 'getting-started', '<p>The communications platform for the enterprise.</p>\n\n<p>Free Demo</p>\n\n<p>Watch a 90 Second Video</p>\n\n<p>An all-in-one platform </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">horn combines video, voice, screen sharing that\'s completely white label, requires no user downloads, and seamlessly folds into your organization\'s site within a few seconds.</span></p>\n\n<p>Features</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Seamlessly embeds in your site in minutes with a widget - and with your branding.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Allows developers to fully integrate horn\'s platform into your products and/or your other systems.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Attendees can view, talk and listen through their browser - without any downloads. Presenters control through an easy to use Chrome extension.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Access on horn\'s site or setup on your own site. Setup is a breeze, and your audience can be talking, typing, and sharing video in no time.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Video, voice and screen easily shared - and can be completely recorded at a click for future reference.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Comprehensive controls for moderator or presenter to easily manage the session.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Lower bandwidth usage with higher quality audio and video.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">High fidelity and clarity, minimizing skips and delays whether you access through your computer or your phone.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">The MIDI Association has built an online user community and needed a way to enhance the connection with those members. With the easy to embed widget, they added horn to create a live forum, answering questions and engaging in real conversations. It also allows them to meet the requests of users to host panel discussions with experts on their favorite topics.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Clockswork\'s graduate courses in finance engage best and brightest learning from experts across the globe. With multiple presenter panels sharing voice, video, screens and materials with dozens of attendees, the classes and webinars are simple for presenters to manage and communications are of the highest quality - thanks to horn.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Yamaha needed a better way to communicate and collaborate as a team. The clarity of sound and consistency of connection - accessible by computer link or mobile app - drives productivity. With one click, voice conferencing becomes as simple as a single call.</span></p>\n\n<p>From Our Blog<br><br></p>\n\n<p>A digital agency Principal shares his experiences in online meeting tools and choosing horn to support the needs of his team and clients.</p>\n\n<p>An online community can provide your clients, students and supporters a way to better engage with you. What does it take? This article provides some ideas for approach and to consider. </p>\n\n<p>You work hard to put your results in a context for investors, analysts and the public. Now how do you make sure the actual call goes without a hitch? </p>\n\n<p>There are best practices for conducting face-to-face meetings - and a different set for those held online. Ideas for optimizing your next meeting.</p>\n\n<p>Presenting and meeting via video conferencing has unique challenges. With the right planning, you can make it smooth for all involved.</p>\n\n<p>Contact Us</p>\n\n<p>Sign-up for a free demo</p>\n\n', '<!-- {\"name\":\"Home\",\"type\":\"layout\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"\",\"type\":\"section\",\"props\":{\"style\":\"default\",\"width\":\"default\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"title_position\":\"top-left\",\"title_rotation\":\"left\",\"title_breakpoint\":\"xl\",\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"image\":